title: Bible (Reina Valera 1909) NT 06: La Epistola del Apostol San Pablo a los Romanos
creator: Reina Valera
description: LibriVox recording of Saint Paul's letter to the Romans, in Spanish. Read by arturo and Karen Savage. La epistola del Apóstol San Pablo a los Romanos, versión Reina Valera. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
